if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e32db90ae9fc4a5d6cd30dfa69945c2ed2db87c","tid":2207398,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b61a057507d6569e8f727e6acd63f4550bd25ed5","tid":2207398,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"完啦司法獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"「有任何人想搞佢既話」"},{"pid":"95443efccdbf45d872d179bb91f3b3bdceb5d323","tid":2207398,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24fe8ff1cb39a5f3a1636ce9f9aebf32babc69a","tid":2207398,"uid":67963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"[回帶] <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.supremecourt.uk/news/role-of-uk-judges-on-the-hong-kong-court-of-final-appeal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supremecourt.uk%2Fnews%2Frole-of-uk-judges-on-the-hong-kong-court-of-final-appeal.html&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdR5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=40b467b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.supremecourt.uk/news/role-of-uk-judges-on-the-hong-kong-court-of-final-appeal.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英國最高法院院長及香港終審庭非常任法官韋彥德勳爵<br />\n2020 年 7 月 17 日通過英國最高法院發表聲明<br />\n指兩地司法機構之首於 1997 年達成協議<br />\n英國上議院 (其後由最高法院取代) 恆常提供兩位大法官予終審庭擔任非常任法官<br />\n但自前英國最高法院院長何熙怡女男爵退休後，香港並無再作委任<br />\n韋彥德本人成為唯一於終審庭在任的英國最高法院大法官<br />\n而今年並無派過 Case 俾任何英國最高法院在任的大法官 (即係佢本人)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">韋彥德指︰<br />\n<br />\n「英國最高法院將繼續支持香港法官守衛司法獨立及法治，但亦會密切留意香港局勢發展，以及同英國政府商討。最終英國最高法院的大法官能可否繼續為香港服務，將取決於其服務是否與司法獨立和法治相乎。」︰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">&quot;The Supreme Court supports the judges of Hong Kong in their commitment to safeguard judicial independence and the rule of law. It will continue to assess the position in Hong Kong as it develops, in discussion with the UK Government. Whether judges of the Supreme Court can continue to serve as judges in Hong Kong will depend on whether such service remains compatible with judicial independence and the rule of law.&quot;</span>"},{"pid":"0bf3c3a11deacfbfcc8624c3375e98cd15190dee","tid":2207398,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"支持但加速唔到跟住就會pk<br />\n希望可以快d衝到到終點"},{"pid":"d655e6a3ec4f506b134f3410f207b0c34b6f84b0","tid":2207398,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee0e351d6090a37713f3c38dbddbbf54d052ab3","tid":2207398,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf3c3a11deacfbfcc8624c3375e98cd15190dee","tid":2207398,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"支持但加速唔到跟住就會pk<br />\n希望可以快d衝到到終點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"冇鬼佬做又點?<br />\n一個錢字D商家佬咪又係奶"},{"pid":"8ff6a316509243256408ae486f78e2b4e52940f3","tid":2207398,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"支持所有外籍法官辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e01952fd075c8edb4f35a6b7dc8b000397bf98","tid":2207398,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"國安法強姦大法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2658ce3a346572fe02a4d3e8414c5d503bcd1b47","tid":2207398,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53487ef009fc820edd37c7870e83de7e20d9ea4a","tid":2207398,"uid":67963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:32:36.000Z","msg":"[回帶] 2019 年英國下議院外交委員會發表名為 「在極權時代守衛民主」(A cautious embrace: defending democracy in an age of autocracies) 的報告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201919/cmselect/cmfaff/109/10902.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201919%2Fcmselect%2Fcmfaff%2F109%2F10902.htm&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdR5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=2e2bbe59\" target=\"_blank\">https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201919/cmselect/cmfaff/109/10902.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n第 39 至 41段提到英國作為在終審庭有法官代表的國家，會否令人聯想到支持削弱法治 (當時嘅送中條例) 。委員會建議與加、澳、紐等國共同回應。"}]}